    <h1>Citation Consistency</h1>
    <p class="description">Ensuring your business NAP matches character-for-character across every directory and platform. Ranks in <strong>Moz's top-10 local ranking factors</strong> and drives up to 6-position local pack lifts inside 45 days when fixed.</p>
